Modifications in this repository
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The files added by this repository (the patch, the helper scripts under
scripts/, the GitHub Actions workflow under .github/workflows/, and the README)
are Copyright the ha-android-authproxy contributors and are likewise licensed
under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (see the LICENSE file).

The patch keeps main-frame authentication-provider navigation inside the app's
WebView so that OIDC / OAuth 2.0 reverse proxies placed in front of Home
Assistant can complete their interactive sign-in. See the README for details,
scope, and known limitations.
